Ext.data.JsonP['Previewing']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Previewing</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083121\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Previewing</h1>\n    <p>Previewing your project means viewing the work you&apos;ve created so far against a local or remote web server. Studio offers a variety of mechanisms to preview your work, depending on your configuration and project type. View the pages below to learn more how to enable the configurations.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083121_Previewing-Chapters\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Chapters</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Previewing_a_project_in_a_web_browser\">Previewing a project in a web browser</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Setting_up_your_web_browser_configuration\">Setting up your web browser configuration</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Side-by-Side_Previewing\">Side-by-Side Previewing</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Creating_a_Custom_Preview_Server\">Creating a Custom Preview Server</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Setting_up_an_external_web_server_to_preview_PHP_and_other_non-HTML_pages\">Setting up an external web server to preview PHP and other non-HTML pages</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083121\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Previewing"});